snippet.title: Mowgli Teaser | Roshan Kanakala | Sandeep Raj | Bandi Saroj Kumar | Sakkshi | TG Vishwa Prasad | PMF
snippet.description:
Mowgli is an upcoming unique romantic action drama set deep within a forest backdrop. Directed by National Award-winning filmmaker Sandeep Raj (Colour Photo), Produced by TG Vishwa Prasad and Krithi Prasad under People Media Factory Banner.The film has cinematography by Rama Maruthi M, while Kaala Bhairava scores the music. The work is co-written by Rama Maruthi M and Radhakrishna Reddy The technical team also includes Peekay as editor, Kiran Mamidi as art director, and Natraj Madigonda choreographing the action sequences.

Mowgli 2025 will arrive in cinemas on December 12th, 2025.

Cast: Roshan Kanakala, Sakkshi Mhadolkar, Bandi Saroj Kumar & Harsha Chemudu

snippet.description:

snippet.title: Chaaha Hai Tujhko Lyrical | Udit Narayan, Anuradha Paudwal | Aamir Khan, Manisha | Mann
snippet.description:
Song Credits:
Song Name : Chaaha Hai Tujhko Lyrical 
Movie Name : Mann
Singer(s): Udit Narayan, Anuradha Paudwal
Music Director: Sanjeev-Darshan
Lyricist: Sameer
Edit & Gfx : Nadeem Akhtar (Paperboyz Studioz)

Movie Cast & Crew:
Producer: Indra Kumar, Ashok Thakeria
Director: Indra Kumar
Cast: Aamir Khan, Manisha Koirala

Song Lyrics:

Chaaha Hai Tujhko Chahunga Har Dam
Marke Bhi Dil Se Yeh Pyaar Na Hoga Kam
Teri Yaad Jo Aati Hai,
Mere Aansu Behete Hain
Apna Toh Milan Hoga,
Pal Pal Yeh Kehte Hain
Kya Yeh Zindagani Hai,
Bas Teri Kahani Hai
Bas Teri Kahani Hai,
Yeh Jo Zindagani Hai
Chaaha Hai Tujhko Chahunga Har Dam
Marke Bhi Dil Se Yeh Pyaar Na Hoga Kam
Teri Woh Baatein
Woh Chhahat Ki Rasmein
Jhuthe The Waade
Kya Jhuthi Thi Kasmein
Jaane Tamannah Kya Yeh Sacch
Hai Bas Itna Kehe De
Tut Jaaye Na Lamha Aitbaar Ka
De Koi Sila Mere Intezaar Ka
Chaaha Hai Tujhko Chahungi Har Dam
Marke Bhi Dil Se Yeh Pyaar Na Hoga Kam
Teri Hu Teri
Jo Chaahe Kasam Le Le
Mujhko Humraahi
Tu Apne Gam De De
Sari Umar Hai Mujhko
Dard Judai Ka Sehena
Raste Mein Khoyi Hai
Manzile Meri
Mere Sath Jayengi
Mushkile Meri
Chaaha Hai Tujhko Chahungahar Dam
Marke Bhi Dil Se Yeh Pyaar Na Hoga Kam
Tu Saamne Hai Mere,
Phir Kyun Yeh Doorie Hai
Tujhe Kaise Bataau Main
Haaye Kya Majburi Hai
Yeh Bhi Koi Jeena Hai
Sirf Aansu Peena Hai
Sirf Aansu Peena Hai
Yeh Bhi Koi Jeena Hai

snippet.description:
#VARANASI to the World - Mahesh Babu | Priyanka Chopra | Prithviraj | SS Rajamouli

Here is our reaction to the teaser of VARANASI, starring Mahesh Babu, Priyanka Chopra Jonas, and Prithviraj Sukumaran. Presented by SS Rajamouli, the film introduces Mahesh Babu as Rudhra ‚Äî a globe-trotting force rising from the spiritual heart of India. Directed by SS Rajamouli, with music by M.M. Keeravaani, Varanasi is produced by KL Narayana and SS Karthikeya under Sri Durga Arts and Showing Business. Watch our full breakdown as we discuss the world-building, performance, visuals, and what this glimpse reveals about the scale and storytelling of this epic.

Presented by SS Rajamouli, the film introduces Mahesh Babu as Rudhra ‚Äî a globe-trotting force rising from the spiritual heart of India. Directed by SS Rajamouli, with music by M.M. The film also marks the maiden production venture of Mr. MRK Jhayaram under his banner Aaradyaa Studios.

snippet.title: The Devil Wears Prada 2 | Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
A sequel? For spring? Groundbreaking. Meryl Streep, Anne Hathaway, Emily Blunt, and Stanley Tucci return in The Devil Wears Prada 2, in theaters May 1, 2026. Watch the teaser trailer now.¬†

Almost twenty years after making their iconic turns as Miranda, Andy, Emily and Nigel‚ÄîMeryl Streep, Anne Hathaway, Emily Blunt and Stanley Tucci return to the fashionable streets of New York City and the sleek offices of Runway Magazine in the eagerly awaited sequel to the 2006 phenomenon that defined a generation. 
 
The film reunites the original main cast with director David Frankel and writer Aline Brosh McKenna, and introduces an all-new runway of characters including Kenneth Branagh, Simone Ashley, Justin Theroux, Lucy Liu, Patrick Brammall, Caleb Hearon, Helen J. Shen, Pauline Chalamet, B.J. Novak and Conrad Ricamora. Tracie Thoms and Tibor Feldman also reprise their roles as ‚ÄúLily‚Äù and ‚ÄúIrv‚Äù from the first film. 
 
‚ÄúThe Devil Wears Prada 2‚Äù is produced by Wendy Finerman, and executive produced by Michael Bederman, Karen Rosenfelt and McKenna. The film debuts exclusively in theaters May 1, 2026.

The thrilling theatrical trailer of ‚Äú12A Railway Colony‚Äù is finally out, and it promises an intense cinematic experience packed with suspense, mystery, and unexpected twists. Directed and edited by Nani Kasaragadda and written by Dr. Anil Viswanath, the creative mind behind Polimera and Polimera 2, the film takes viewers on a gripping journey through secrets hidden in the shadows of a quiet railway colony. Backed by Srinivasaa Silver Screen and produced by Srinivasaa Chitturi, with Pavan Kumar presenting, the film‚Äôs visuals and edge-of-the-seat narrative are already generating buzz among thriller lovers.

Set to release worldwide in theatres on November 21, 12A Railway Colony is poised to be one of the most talked-about Telugu thrillers of 2025. With its intriguing storyline, stellar direction, and powerful performances, the film promises a rollercoaster of emotions, suspense, and drama. Don‚Äôt miss this must-watch suspense thriller that will keep you guessing until the very last frame ‚Äî 12A Railway Colony, where every twist hides a deeper secret.

snippet.title: Love You Papa | Projapati 2 | Mithun C | Dev | Ishan | Jeet Gannguli | Avijit Senn | ‚Ä™Bengal Talkies
snippet.description:
Presenting the official video of ‚ÄúLove You Papa‚Äù from the much-awaited film Projapati 2‚Äîa heartfelt tribute to the unspoken bond between a father and child. The song beautifully captures the warmth and love that shape a family‚Äôs journey. With its touching lyrics and soulful melody, ‚ÄúLove You Papa‚Äù feels like a gentle reminder of the moments we often take for granted. The visuals add an emotional depth, portraying everyday memories that feel real, relatable, and deeply nostalgic.
 
Whether you‚Äôre watching with family or listening alone, this song leaves a soft ache in the heart and a smile on the face. It‚Äôs the kind of track that lingers long after it ends‚Äîperfect for anyone who cherishes the timeless connection between a father and child.

"Tu Cheez Badi Hai Mast Mast" is a popular Bollywood song from the 1994 film Mohra. The track was sung by Udit Narayan and Kavita Krishnamurthy, with music composed by Viju Shah and lyrics penned by Anand Bakshi. The song became iconic for its catchy beat and energetic vocals, and it features the legendary performances of actors Akshay Kumar and Raveen Tondon.

snippet.title: HUM BAS TERE HAIN - Ek Deewane Ki Deewaniyat | Harshvardhan & Sonam | B Praak, Rahul, Rish & Prince
snippet.description:
Teri Deewaniyat mein guzre din mere hain, #HumBasTereHain
‚ù§Ô∏è‚Äçüî• Song out now

#EkDeewaneKiDEEWANIYAT Booking open: https://bookmy.show/HI_EDKD

In Cinemas Now!

Song : Hum bas tere hain 
Music : Rahul Mishra 
Lyrics : Prince Dubey 
Singer : B Praak
Music producer : The Rish

PlayDMF Team :-
Founder & CEO : Anshul Garg  
Vice President : Raghav Sharma ( Pratick Sharma)
Label Manager : Sankalp Garg
Project & Artist Manager : Gaurav Arora
Legal & Digital Manager : Ashima Chauhan
PlayDMF Team : Aansi Agrawal & Anshu Prasad
Artwork : Vicky Sandhu
Special Thanks : Virgin Music India

Virgin Music India Team :-
Head : Amit Sharma 
Team : Nagesh Jadhav, Kajal Israni, Amol Suryavanshi, Lavanya Das & Nishtha Sikroria

https://www.virginmusic.com/

Lyrics :-
Chaahe ye zamana badal bhi jaaye
Aa jaaye yahan daur koi
Dil mein hamesha tum hi rahoge
Na aayega aur koi 

Hum bas tere hain 
Jab tak jiyenge tere hi rahenge
Hum ye kah rahe hain
Hum toh tere hain tere hi rahenge 

Rasta ek ho tera mera yahan 
Maangta hoon main aur kuch bhi Kahan
Tu mujhe jo mile dard mere hansenge 
Kaash mujhko tu bhi yun hi chaahta 

Haar jaaun kahin toh junoon tu bane
Zindagi bhar ka mere sukoon tu bane 

Ab meri shaamein mere savere
Honge na tere bagair koi 
Dil mein hamesha tum hi rahoge 
Na aayega aur koi 
Hum bas tere hain 
Jab tak jiyenge tere hi rahenge 
Hum ye kah rahe hain 
Hum toh tere hain tere hi rahenge

#HarshvardhanRane #SonamBajwa #DeewaniyatKiDiwali #Diwali2025.

snippet.title: Naezy | Area Mein Dhoor | Alter EP
snippet.description:
prod. by Uzi Music 
Lyrics, Concept, - Naezy 

Aisa area sab darte naam se
Yaha ghumega jayega kaam se sada rehta mai yaha Shaan se
khoonkhar jeev hood pe Paalte 
beta yaha chalna araam se 
lafa tere niche Kaan k 
band kar maarenge taang k Aafat ab teri Jaan pe
arey bhai Mai toh tehel raha tha
Bahana tera nahi chalega 
yaha tak tu kaise pohcha 
Ang par tere rokda hai kya 
Tone me tere khopra hai kya  hood enter konsa kiya 
sannata phir goojenga madad phir tu dhundega auzar hote roz Dhaar yaha pe
mazdoor paate rozgar yaha pe
dushman ko bhi mile pyaar yaha pe
Lekin Bache nahi bin bulaye mehman
yeh koi tafri ki jaga nahi
awaragardi ko panah nahi hosh me aa beta tu hasa nahi 
Idhar kya Karra tha chal Bata bhai
bhai Mai toh bas Dekh raha tha
aankhien teri ab footegi Ladkiyan yaha parda karti Kuch ladke garda karte 
Jo koi yaha sab adab me fokut mat aa magaj pe
matter yaha Har sadak pe 
bhai lo na tum samaj k
ruk tujhe aibalog k karta hawale
aibalog pasli tode saamaan nikale
mamalog asli saare jag me misal hai 
Beta yeh bambai ki chawl hai Sidha bawal hai
Aur ek toh tu yaha ka Naya chawal hai 
Khatir me kami nahi sada bahar hai 
Neech harkat kara toh phir baja guitar hai 
Lekin mai kyu aunga
mere paas toh car hai 
ek kaam kar chal wata
mujhe car ka ek round ghuma 
Nahi lagaunga tujhe chuna
Nahi aaj koi karunga gunah
hood khatarnaak lekin mohabbat pehle
Dhoor phasti roz
dehshat fayle
mood badle mehfil
baithak chale
door bajte dhol ache
Nazdeek nahi re 
ek number chiz
hood ki tameez
fayda kya tera yaha latak kar 
Hua Jo Shaheed
wo swargwasi
kya mangta bol tu sirf awaz kar
Kaam pachchis
dial 0 shambar bhi 
Hold apna khatri kya aa sattar 
Wyawhar marzi
ateethi habib 
Area ki dhoor saab namaskar
